::Reptilica::

"Interesting," Reptilica finishes Feline's sentance. He frowns.

"Thats one wierd spider. I think you should have Squizzy take a look 
at that."



--- In nbwrpg@y..., logomorph@h... wrote:
> Feline::
> 
> She heard Reptilica. Perhaps she hadn't lost her touch yet. 
> "I was getting the DNA samples, then got bit by a strange spider.  
> Shortly there after, my skin fell off my frame. So, here I am, no 
> real beast mode and peltless. Just look at me, look at me, I'm, uh, 
> well," she said, feeling her face flush into a red,"I'm without a 
> pelt to cover my frame. It's, it's, it's...."  she couldn't bring 
> herself to finish that thought.
